{
  "text": "Increasing transparency has a positive effect on consumption efficiency. This is intuitive. As price goes closer to marginal cost consumption efficiency increases. Note that this effect is not present in the analysis by [CITATION_1] .",
  "correct_citation": {
    "[CITATION_1]": "154707580"
